t": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.347680", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "6": {"media_key": "202305/17977097138326721", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202305/17977097138326721.jpg", "filename": "17977097138326721.jpg", "date_folder": "202305", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.352872", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "7": {"media_key": "202305/17981297990157244", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202305/17981297990157244.jpg", "filename": "17981297990157244.jpg", "date_folder": "202305", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.357401", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "8": {"media_key": "202305/17994657838788708", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202305/17994657838788708.jpg", "filename": "17994657838788708.jpg", "date_folder": "202305", "caption": "Sorry my English friends, i can't express my feeling enough in English. My love for my wife has to be expressed in my native language. (But you can always translate)\n\nHoy es un d\u00c3\u00ada muy especial, es nuestra celebraci\u00c3\u00b3n de aniversario con la persona que mas amo en el mundo, la persona con la quiero estar siempre, mi mejor amiga, mi compa\u00c3\u00b1era de vida. La persona con la que me puedo embarcar en cualquier aventura y saber que lo haremos juntos con amor.\nEn estos 14 a\u00c3\u00b1os hemos crecido juntos en nuestro amor, acompa\u00c3\u00b1\u00c3\u00a1ndonos, queri\u00c3\u00a9ndonos, cuid\u00c3\u00a1ndonos, respet\u00c3\u00a1ndonos y am\u00c3\u00a1ndonos.\nHemos tenido aventura tras aventura, pero en todas juntos. Por que eres la persona me hace feliz, que me haces sentir mariposas, que me enamoras que me encanta.\nEste 14vo aniversario es el primero que tambi\u00c3\u00a9n celebramos como matrimonio, no es que lo necesit\u00c3\u00a1ramos, lo quer\u00c3\u00adamos, porque independientemente del estado, nuestro amor es grande, constante y creciente.\nEres la mejor compa\u00c3\u00b1era, eres la mejor persona con la que quiero estar.\nTe amo hoy, te amo ma\u00c3\u00b1ana, te am\u00c3\u00a9 ayer y te amar\u00c3\u00a9 siempre mi hermosa esposa.\n\nFeliz 14 aniversario juntos.\nFeliz primer aniversario de matrimonio", "created_at": "2023-05-19T11:55:35", "creation_timestamp": 1684511735, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.362920", "post_url": null}, "9": {"media_key": "202305/18365697388038837", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202305/18365697388038837.jpg", "filename": "18365697388038837.jpg", "date_folder": "202305", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.367766", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "10": {"media_key": "202307/17889019142800763", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202307/17889019142800763.jpg", "filename": "17889019142800763.jpg", "date_folder": "202307", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.373362", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "11": {"media_key": "202312/17867897577046215", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202312/17867897577046215.jpg", "filename": "17867897577046215.jpg", "date_folder": "202312", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.377984", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "12": {"media_key": "202312/17990346980592022", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202312/17990346980592022.jpg", "filename": "17990346980592022.jpg", "date_folder": "202312", "caption": "Hoy es el cumplea\u00c3\u00b1os de la persona que m\u00c3\u00a1s amo en este mundo.\nCon la que cumplimos sue\u00c3\u00b1os juntos, con la que nos acompa\u00c3\u00b1amos en esta vida y con la que quiero estar siempre.\nFeliz cumplea\u00c3\u00b1os mi amor de mi vida. Eres lo m\u00c3\u00a1s importante y lo que m\u00c3\u00a1s quiero y amo.\nTe amo de aqu\u00c3\u00ad al infinito y a\u00c3\u00ban as\u00c3\u00ad queda corto.\nFelices 29 a\u00c3\u00b1os. Feliz de estar contigo. Feliz de celebrarte.\n\nTe amo mi hermosa marida \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f", "created_at": "2023-12-29T09:12:17", "creation_timestamp": 1703859137, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.383221", "post_url": null}, "13": {"media_key": "202312/17994710375452118", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202312/17994710375452118.jpg", "filename": "17994710375452118.jpg", "date_folder": "202312", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.388449", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "14": {"media_key": "202312/18000149288362983", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202312/18000149288362983.jpg", "filename": "18000149288362983.jpg", "date_folder": "202312", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.393514", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "15": {"media_key": "202312/18018862000799775", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202312/18018862000799775.jpg", "filename": "18018862000799775.jpg", "date_folder": "202312", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at":