: null}, "113": {"media_key": "202405/18034904629748899", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18034904629748899.jpg", "filename": "18034904629748899.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.920722", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "114": {"media_key": "202405/18041151397875063", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18041151397875063.jpg", "filename": "18041151397875063.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "caption": "Hot day in Santiago.\nRe-seeing the same city with different eyes.\n.\n.\n.\nLeica m10 | Zeiss 35mm Biogon\n#leica #street #streetphotography #retinalatinxs", "created_at": "2024-05-25T23:24:50", "creation_timestamp": 1716693890, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.925950", "post_url": null}, "115": {"media_key": "202405/18049638199713956", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18049638199713956.jpg", "filename": "18049638199713956.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.931228", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "116": {"media_key": "202405/18050849191575973", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18050849191575973.jpg", "filename": "18050849191575973.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.938290", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "117": {"media_key": "202405/18081864526461500", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18081864526461500.jpg", "filename": "18081864526461500.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.943441", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "118": {"media_key": "202405/18083161531456470", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18083161531456470.jpg", "filename": "18083161531456470.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "caption": "Cada d\u00c3\u00ada m\u00c3\u00a1s y m\u00c3\u00a1s enamorado de ti,\nDe tu compa\u00c3\u00b1\u00c3\u00ada,\nDe tu sonrisa,\nDe tu ser\nDe tu amor\nFeliz de celebrar estos 15 a\u00c3\u00b1os juntos, la mitad de mi vida contigo. 15 a\u00c3\u00b1os de amor, compa\u00c3\u00b1\u00c3\u00ada, aventuras, risas y cari\u00c3\u00b1os.\nNo puedo esperar a que m\u00c3\u00a1s nos depara el resto de la vida juntos.\nTe amo por todo, te amo con todo \nTe amo siempre \u00f0\u009f\u00a5\u00b0\n\n\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\u00e2\u0080\u0094\n\nEveryday more and more in love with you,\nOf your company,\nOf your smile,\nOf your being\nOf your love\nHappy to celebrate these 15 years together, half my life with you. 15 years of love, company, adventures, laughter and more love.\nI can\u00e2\u0080\u0099t wait for the rest of our lives together.\nI love you for everything, I love you with everything \nI love you always \u00f0\u009f\u00a5\u00b0", "created_at": "2024-05-19T10:18:27", "creation_timestamp": 1716128307, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.949489", "post_url": null}, "119": {"media_key": "202405/18085292164413423", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18085292164413423.jpg", "filename": "18085292164413423.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.954671", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "120": {"media_key": "202405/18085890730456455", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18085890730456455.jpg", "filename": "18085890730456455.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.959921", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "121": {"media_key": "202405/18100463434394328", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18100463434394328.jpg", "filename": "18100463434394328.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.966208", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "122": {"media_key": "202405/18128102605345110", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18128102605345110.jpg", "filename": "18128102605345110.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.971610", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "123": {"media_key": "202405/18227118982286117", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18227118982286117.jpg", "filename": "18227118982286117.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:18.977938", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "124": {"media_key": "202405/18227438278285014", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202405/18227438278285014.jpg", "filename": "18227438278285014.jpg", "date_folder": "202405", "caption": "Just light on 