: "Llevamos 16 a\u00c3\u00b1os de historia juntos. Y 3 estos de matrimonio y todav\u00c3\u00ada nos queda mucho por compartir y crear juntos. \nEres el amor de mi vida y por siempre lo ser\u00c3\u00a1s. Un amor aut\u00c3\u00a9ntico, apa\u00c3\u00b1ador, fuerte y cari\u00c3\u00b1oso.\nTe amo, te amo y te amo mi eterna compa\u00c3\u00b1era de vida.\n.\n.\n.\nWe\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve shared 16 years of history together.\nAnd 3 of marriage- yet we still have so much more to share and create.\nYou are the love of my life and always will be.\nA love that\u00e2\u0080\u0099s authentic, resilient, strong and tender.\nI love you, I love you, l love you... my eternal partner in life", "created_at": "2025-05-19T12:25:51", "creation_timestamp": 1747671951, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.077891", "post_url": null}, "302": {"media_key": "202505/18062865629040306", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202505/18062865629040306.jpg", "filename": "18062865629040306.jpg", "date_folder": "202505", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.084880", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "303": {"media_key": "202505/18063200543097623", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202505/18063200543097623.jpg", "filename": "18063200543097623.jpg", "date_folder": "202505", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.091132", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "304": {"media_key": "202505/18067266700792257", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202505/18067266700792257.jpg", "filename": "18067266700792257.jpg", "date_folder": "202505", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": 