202512/18062248433542985", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202512/18062248433542985.jpg", "filename": "18062248433542985.jpg", "date_folder": "202512", "caption": "More from New York City earlier this year.\n.\n.\n.\nLeica m10 | Zeiss Biogon 35mm", "created_at": "2025-12-03T21:34:21", "creation_timestamp": 1764815661, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.482858", "post_url": null}, "362": {"media_key": "202512/18083094326169417", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202512/18083094326169417.jpg", "filename": "18083094326169417.jpg", "date_folder": "202512", "caption": "Carrusel de fotos anual de apreciaci\u00c3\u00b3n a mi hermosa hermosa esposa que cumple a\u00c3\u00b1os el d\u00c3\u00ada de hoy.\nTe amo y estoy muy feliz de compartir contigo mi vida. \nFeliz cumplea\u00c3\u00b1os amada m\u00c3\u00ada, eres una mujer maravillosa! Y amo cada momento contigo.\nHa sido un a\u00c3\u00b1o de muchos logros para ti y profunda admiraci\u00c3\u00b3n de mi hacia ti! De verte cumplirlos y de verte crecer.\nTe amo, te amo y te amo \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f", "created_at": "2025-12-29T11:22:11", "creation_timestamp": 1767025331, "exif_data": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.489445", "post_url": null}, "363": {"media_key": "202512/18090845281909779", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/posts/202512/18090845281909779.jpg", "filename": "18090845281909779.jpg", "date_folder": "202512", "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:20.496559", "exif_data": null, "post_url": null}, "364": {"media_key": "202512/18091972802312939", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-du