more than 9000 km away from there \u00f0\u009f\u0098\u0085\nThis specific trekking was on the way to Cerro Trinidad at the Valley.\n.\n.\n#cochamo #blackandwhite #blackandwhitephotography #fujixpro2 \nFuji xpro2 || fujicron 23mm", "created_at": "2023-01-23T19:29:45", "creation_timestamp": 1674520185, "exif_data": {"latitude": -41.493382, "longitude": -72.307101}, "exif_date_time_original": null, "exif_latitude": -41.493382, "exif_longitude": -72.307101, "exif_device_id": null, "exif_lens_model": null, "exif_iso": null, "exif_aperture": null, "exif_shutter_speed": null, "exif_focal_length": null, "exif_lens_make": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:21.867831", "post_url": null}, "542": {"media_key": "other/18234197962106859", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/other/18234197962106859.jpg", "filename": "18234197962106859.jpg", "date_folder": null, "caption": "Document your family is one of the things that I most love about photography.\nThis is a member of our family. Our little dog called Lupin. Is 5 years old but have the souls of a puppy.\n.\n.\n.\nPentax spotmatic || fomapan 400\n#film #filmphotography #filmpotrait #dog  #family", "created_at": "2022-05-09T17:38:33", "creation_timestamp": 1652132313, "exif_data": {"latitude": -33.45521, "longitude": -70.59388}, "exif_date_time_original": null, "exif_latitude": -33.45521, "exif_longitude": -70.59388, "exif_device_id": null, "exif_lens_model": null, "exif_iso": null, "exif_aperture": null, "exif_shutter_speed": null, "exif_focal_length": null, "exif_lens_make": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:21.876289", "post_url": null}, "543": {"media_key": "other/18313623025099670", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/other/18313623025099670.jpg", "filename": "18313623025099670.jpg", "date_folder": null, "caption": "*English below*\n\nEl 18 de octubre de 2021 esta foto fue tomada. Cuando est\u00c3\u00a1bamos luchando por un nuevo cambio, uno donde las cosas estaban bien distribuidas.\nLuchando por lo que qued\u00c3\u00b3 despu\u00c3\u00a9s de la dictadura que comenz\u00c3\u00b3 hace 50 a\u00c3\u00b1os.\nCuando miles fueron asesinados por la \u00c3\u00banica raz\u00c3\u00b3n de pensar diferente.\nHace 50 a\u00c3\u00b1os, Estados Unidos y Pinochet determinaron el futuro de miles.\n50 a\u00c3\u00b1os y siguen desaparecidos, no nos dicen d\u00c3\u00b3nde los entierran.\n50 a\u00c3\u00b1os y algunos todav\u00c3\u00ada justifican esas acciones.\n\n//\n\nOn Oct 18 2021 this photo was taken. When we were fighting for a new change, one where things were well distributed.\nFighting for what was left after the dictatorship that began 50 years ago.\nWhen thousands were killed for the mere reason of only think different.\n50 years ago USA and Pinochet determined the future of thousands.\n50 years and they are still missing, They don't tell us where they bury them.\n50 years and some still justify those actions.\n.\n.\n.\n.\nPara que nunca m\u00c3\u00a1s en Chile.", "created_at": "2023-09-11T21:10:15", "creation_timestamp": 1694481015, "exif_data": {"latitude": -33.43715333, "longitude": -70.63453667}, "exif_date_time_original": null, "exif_latitude": -33.43715333, "exif_longitude": -70.63453667, "exif_device_id": null, "exif_lens_model": null, "exif_iso": null, "exif_aperture": null, "exif_shutter_speed": null, "exif_focal_length": null, "exif_lens_make": null, "processed": false, "matched_catalog_key": null, "vision_result": null, "vision_score": null, "processed_at": null, "added_at": "2026-03-21T22:47:21.885026", "post_url": null}, "544": {"media_key": "other/18317644759059180", "file_path": "/home/cristian/instagram-dump/media/other/18317644759059180.jpg", "filename": "18317644759059180.jpg", "date_folder": null, "caption": "My beautiful